		<speach name = "K" exp = "surprise" type = "speach">天呐，我什么都不记得了。</speach>
		<speach name = "K" exp = "think" type = "speach">有人吗？</speach>
    <speach name = "K" exp = "angry" type = "speach">或者有办法可以出去吗？</speach>
		<speach name = "K" exp = "think" type = "speach">或许我应该四处调查一番，看看能够发现什么。</speach>
    <speach name = "" exp = "" type = "tutorial">教学1：将鼠标移动至屏幕两侧以显示箭头。长按箭头向相应的方向移动。</speach>
	</event>
